00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:41,559
Bunuh saja aku!

104
00:07:42,169 --> 00:07:44,470
Aku muak dengan ini!

105
00:07:44,669 --> 00:07:45,970
- Bunuh aku!
- Bunuh aku!

106
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,169
Minggir!

107
00:08:32,749 --> 00:08:34,580
Mereka sudah pergi.

